  <brief_title>Barrett's Esophagus - 315 - 3 Way Cross-Over</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multicenter, Double-blind, Three-way Crossover Intraesophageal and Intragastric pH Study of Three Esomeprazole Treatment Regimens in Documented Barrett's Esophagus Patients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>AstraZeneca</agency>
      <agency_class>Industry</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>AstraZeneca</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study looks the intragastric and intraesophageal pH in patients with documented
      Barrett's esophagus whilst taking esomeprazole 40mg twice daily, esomeprazole 40mg three
      times daily, esomeprazole 20 mg three times daily.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
